title: About me
text: My name is Alaina, and I am a third-year student at the University of Toronto. I am studying economics, psychology, and statistics. I am passionate about problem-solving and relationship-building. Through my academic courses, personal projects, and extracurriculars, I have been able to grow my skills in these areas. In my free time, I love spending time with friends, listening to music, or exercising.
